    "Name": "Scatter Plas",
    "Details": "We here at QuickSell know you're looking for the best weapons out there. And we hear you! Boy, those Battlearmor and infantry are annoying, right? So we came up with hollow-point plasma cartridges, providing the *oomph* of a hollow-point, with the *sizzle* of Plasma. You might say that's totally insane, but we find that the hollow-point design helps to spread the plasma around, turning a single ball of burny, into many balls of you-should-have-stayed-home!* <size=80%>*Warning: Firing non-lased hollow-point plasma cartridges constitutes a war crime according to the updated Ares convention of 3298. Always excite your cartridges, and we mean with lasers.<size=100%> \n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Uses Plasma Ammo.</color></b> <b><color=#099ff2>VOLATILE!</color></b>",
